                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9568" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1444</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">939 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">风口上的“中药+”：传承百黎堂匠心，开创陆藜风华</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The &quot;Herbal Medicine+&quot; Trend: Upholding the Craftsmanship of Bailitang, Creating the Elegance of Luli</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王爱群，张格格</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">吉林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏百黎堂健康管理有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陆藜开了个方子；品牌传承；文化营销；价值共创</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Lu Li&#39;s Formulations;Brand Inheritance;Cultural Marketing;Value Co-Creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，随着年轻一代健康养生意识的增强，“中药+”餐饮业态不断涌现。2023年，百黎堂推出了陆藜开了个方子的奶茶品牌，品牌凭借一杯“中药奶茶”吸引了追求“朋克养生”的年轻消费者，成功开辟了中药养生草本茶饮的细分市场。自品牌创立以来，陆藜开了个方子迅速发展，截至2024年已在全国布局超过200家线下门店，覆盖了20多个省份。本案例围绕陆藜开了个方子的初创经历、品牌精准定位、形象塑造及营销策略，描述了该品牌在激烈的新茶饮市场中如何通过市场细分策略获得突破，以及品牌面临的质疑。通过本案例的学习，引导学生了解宏观环境对企业的影响，掌握品牌定位、品牌营销策略等理论知识，思考陆藜开了个方子未来要如何实现持续成长并给出建议，提高学生分析和解决问题的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, with the growing health awareness among younger generations, the &quot;Traditional Chinese Medicine (TCM) +&quot; concept has gained increasing momentum in the food and beverage industry. In 2023, &quot;Lu Li&#39;s Formulations &quot; attracted health-conscious young consumers with its innovative &quot;TCM milk tea,&quot; successfully establishing a niche in the herbal tea market for TCM-based health beverages. Since its inception, the brand has expanded rapidly, operating over 200 physical stores across more than 20 provinces in China by 2024. It describes how the brand has achieved breakthroughs in the competitive new tea beverage market through effective market segmentation strategies while also addressing the criticisms it faces. Through this study, students will gain insights into the impact of the macroeconomic environment on businesses and acquire theoretical knowledge of brand positioning and marketing strategies. Additionally, they will reflect on how Lu Li&#39;s Formulations can achieve sustainable growth in the future and provide recommendations, thereby enhancing their analytical and problem-solving skills.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《品牌管理》、《品牌定位》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">品牌定位；价值共创理论；品牌传承理论；文化营销理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-04</td>
